description:
On today’s show, Dr. Emily is giving all the tips & tricks you need in order to keep the spark alive in a long distance relationship, because sex & intimacy can prevail no matter the distance! Plus, she’s answering your questions. 

She shares all the LDR sex hacks such as sexting, FaceTime dates, even to controlling vibrator speeds overseas! Plus, how to recreate the elusive squirting experience you once had with your husband, & ways to overcome brainblocking during sex & relax in the bedroom. 


Follow Emily on all social: @sexwithemily

For even more sex talk, tips, & tricks visit sexwithemily.com
